<bioghist encodinganalog="545">
<p>Emmet O. Allen was born May 24, 1846 in Bridgewater Township, Washtenaw County, Michigan.  His family had recently moved from New York State.  He attended a rural school close to his home, also a school at Clinton and Ypsilanti, Michigan.  As a young man, he lived in Kansas for a time, but then came back to Michigan.  In 1881, he married Elizabeth (Libbie) Howell.  Both he and his wife were teachers.</p>
</bioghist>

<scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
<p>This family collection is divided into the following series: William F. Allen; Emmet O. Allen; Elizabeth Howell Allen; Matthew Howell; and Photographs</p>
</scopecontent>

